casebody.data:
PEOPLE S256568 Supreme Court of California. AUGUST 28, 2019

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar, Kruger and Groban, JJ.

GALINDO

The petition for review is granted. Further action in this matter is deferred pending consideration and disposition of a related issue in People v. Kelly, S255145, and People v. Stamps, S255843 (see Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.512(d)(2) ), or pending further order of the court. Submission of additional briefing, pursuant to California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of the court.
